    protected final class IndexedLinkManager.LinkFilter
extends AndFilter<T>
implements IndexedLinkManager.LinkProvider<T,L,R>
    Filter for link objects This class handles filtering by the end points and can be extended by composition for example to select objects with a particular status. This class also initialises the cache links for the objects it knows about if its the top level filter.
